Create HourglassLoader that uses HourgldassWidget
internally. 
It should display hourglass animation as
AnimatedHourglass does, but when animation is finished,
hourglass should be rotated 180 degree and animation
should restart. 

It should has following parameters (all named
and optional): 
1. duration - duration of hourglass animation 
(default 3 sec)
2. width (default 100)
3. height (default 150)
4. topBottomColor - the color of top and bottom lines
  (default Color(0xFFA0A0A0).withValues(alpha: 0.6))
5. glassColor - the color of the hourglass
   (default Color(0xFFB8E6E8).withValues(alpha: 0.6)) 
6. sandColor 
   (default Color(0xFFF4A460))    